data.value:
1. Login with: Username: root Password: dbps 2. Choose "Configuration menu" > "serial ports" > Click on the "Port 1"link > Click on '‘Change Profile…'’ > Select the “Industrial Automation” > click the "Apply" button
3. Verify the Modbus settings: > ‘Forward incoming network requests using’ unit addresses 1 to 247 > ‘Override the Modbus unit address’ checked, and address set to 1.
4. Click "Apply" Button & Reboot.
